flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic demand forecast update or significant supply chain event.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest demand forecast data from SAP S/4HANA]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Run demand fluctuation capacity impact modeling]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: AutoML - Simulate production scenarios under capacity constraints]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: RCA Service - Assess capacity impact of potential disruptions]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: Remote Functions - Perform ROI analysis for capacity investments]
  N5 --> N6{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Present optimal capacity scenarios and investment decisions}
  N6 -->|Primary| P1[Action: Automatically adjust capacity plans, investments, and risk responses based on modeled scenarios.]
  P1 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS and increased EBITDA through preemptive capacity adjustments and optimized investments.]
  N6 -->|High demand variance detected| B1[Trigger additional capacity investment analysis]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Recommend and prioritize capacity expansion projects]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|Significant supply chain disruption i...| B2[Initiate emergency capacity reassignment and rerouting]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Adjust production lines and carrier assignments to mitigate disruption impact]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|Low ROI for proposed capacity investm...| B3[Recommend alternative investment strategies]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Optimize capital allocation to maximize EBITDA impact]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]